		<item>
			<title>Geo Category Overview Module</title>
			<link>http://www.sigsiu.net/download/modules/geo_category_overview.html</link>
			<description> The Sobi2 Geo Category Overview Module shows a Google Map with markers of the Sobi2 entries. 


 Use this Joomla! module to show a Google map with markers of the Sobi2 entries on your site. In the category views only the markers of the entries in the corresponding category are shown - on all other Sobi2 pages all entries are shown.In empty categories or in categories with entries without geographical coordinates an empty map is shown (adjustable).

Show the Google Map also on non Sobi2 pages. It is individually adaptable through various settings in the module administration.

Create your own template for the bubble shown on the map. Show additional information like the address or an image of your entry in the bubble.

Bored by the standard marker? Use an individual marker image for the whole map or even different individual marker images for each category.

Various additional settings are available in the module administration to change the size of the map and to adapt the map control buttons, the zoom level and the map type to your Internet site. For each category, different zoom and center point coordinates can be entered. Also the zoom level and center points can be determined automatically depending on the shown entries.

If you have a lot of entries in a category, the server and browser load increases. Therefore the module has the possibility to limit the number of shown markers. The shown markers are chosen randomly.</description>
